$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
get_room_size

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
get_room_size -  This method returns the room size for a given room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int get_room_size(string file,
int level)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^file%^RESET%^ - the file name of the room
%^BOLD%^level%^RESET%^ - the recursion level
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the size of the room

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/terrain_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the room size for a given room. It uses a cache
to speed things up.
.EP

